43.name: A Trail Leading to the Village
desc: "   You are walking along a dusty road.  It's easier
than travelling in the grasslands.  Just here you see
a small trail leading to a hill to the south where there
is some sort of construction.
To the north you can see the main road leading
both east and west.

147.name: Near A Large Wall
desc: "   You are walking along a grassy plain.  The grass
grows up to the boundary of a large town, it's walls
rising up from the grass.  You do not see anyway in
from here.
